<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Vendor Application Received</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .logo {
            color: #2e7d32;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .content {
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            border-left: 4px solid #2e7d32;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #777;
        }
        .highlight {
            color: #2e7d32;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .details {
            margin: 20px 0;
            padding: 15px;
            background-color: #e8f5e9;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #2e7d32;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <div class="logo">Your Business Platform</div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <h2>Hello {{ownerName}},</h2>
        
        <p>Thank you for submitting your vendor application for <span class="highlight">{{businessName}}</span>.</p>
        
        <p>We've received your application and our team will review it shortly. Here's a summary of the information you provided:</p>
        
        <div class="details">
            <p><strong>Business Name:</strong> {{businessName}}</p>
            <p><strong>Business Location:</strong> {{constituencyName}}</p>
            <p><strong>Contact Number:</strong> {{businessContact}}</p>
        </div>
        
        <p>Our next steps will include:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Reviewing your application details</li>
            <li>Scheduling a physical verification visit from our team</li>
            <li>Contacting you for any additional information if needed</li>
        </ul>
        
        <p>You can expect to hear from us within 3-5 business days. If you have any urgent questions, please don't hesitate to contact our support team.</p>
        
        <p>Thank you for choosing our platform!</p>
        
        <p>Best regards,<br>
        The Vendor Approval Team</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>Â© {{currentYear}} Your Business Platform. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>